    - rid: 5530781209756172512
      type: {class: DistributedUIDGenerator, ns: UnityEngine.Localization.Tables, asm: Unity.Localization}
      data:
        m_CustomEpoch: 1762747152942
    - rid: 5530781212759556111
      type: {class: Comment, ns: UnityEngine.Localization.Metadata, asm: Unity.Localization}
      data:
        m_CommentText: 'Room title used on map and room list. Short label shown on
          room tiles. Max 20 characters. No trailing punctuation. Tone: neutral and
          concise.'
    - rid: 5530781212759556112
      type: {class: Comment, ns: UnityEngine.Localization.Metadata, asm: Unity.Localization}
      data:
        m_CommentText: Room description shown in room details panel or tooltip. Explains
          purpose or tips for the room. Use imperative mood for directives. Max ~120
          characters. No formatting tags unless documented.
    - rid: 5530781212759556113
      type: {class: Comment, ns: UnityEngine.Localization.Metadata, asm: Unity.Localization}
      data:
        m_CommentText: Room title used on map and list. Keep concise. Max 20 characters.
    - rid: 5530781212759556114
      type: {class: Comment, ns: UnityEngine.Localization.Metadata, asm: Unity.Localization}
      data:
        m_CommentText: Description for a normal combat room. Explain objective succinctly
          (e.g., defeat enemies). Max ~120 characters. Prefer imperative phrasing.
    - rid: 5530781212759556115
      type: {class: Comment, ns: UnityEngine.Localization.Metadata, asm: Unity.Localization}
      data:
        m_CommentText: Room title for laboratory-type rooms. Short label; max 20
          characters. Indicate special mechanics if needed.
    - rid: 5530781212759556116
      type: {class: Comment, ns: UnityEngine.Localization.Metadata, asm: Unity.Localization}
      data:
        m_CommentText: Description for laboratory rooms. Mention hazards/special
          mechanics. Provide usage hints if necessary. Max ~120 characters.
    - rid: 5530781212759556117
      type: {class: Comment, ns: UnityEngine.Localization.Metadata, asm: Unity.Localization}
      data:
        m_CommentText: Room title for arena/colosseum. Short label; max 20 characters.
          Indicates combat challenge.
    - rid: 5530781212759556118
      type: {class: Comment, ns: UnityEngine.Localization.Metadata, asm: Unity.Localization}
      data:
        m_CommentText: Description for colosseum/arena rooms. Explain challenge type
          (e.g., consecutive fights) and rewards. Max ~120 characters.
    - rid: 5530781212759556119
      type: {class: Comment, ns: UnityEngine.Localization.Metadata, asm: Unity.Localization}
      data:
        m_CommentText: Room title for shop. Single-word label preferred. Max 12-15
          characters for UI fit.
    - rid: 5530781212759556120
      type: {class: Comment, ns: UnityEngine.Localization.Metadata, asm: Unity.Localization}
      data:
        m_CommentText: Description for shop rooms. Explain what players can buy or
          exchange (credits, items). Max ~120 characters. Do not include currency
          symbol assumptions unless specified.
    - rid: 5530781212759556121
      type: {class: Comment, ns: UnityEngine.Localization.Metadata, asm: Unity.Localization}
      data:
        m_CommentText: Room title for boss encounters. Short label; max 20 characters.
          Indicate high difficulty.
    - rid: 5530781212759556122
      type: {class: Comment, ns: UnityEngine.Localization.Metadata, asm: Unity.Localization}
      data:
        m_CommentText: Description for boss rooms. Warn players about high difficulty;
          advise preparation. Max ~120 characters. Use imperative suggestions (prepare,
          strategize).
    - rid: 5530781212759556335
      type: {class: Comment, ns: UnityEngine.Localization.Metadata, asm: Unity.Localization}
      data:
        m_CommentText: Title for credit currency shown in UI (reward list, popup).
          Keep short (<=12 chars). Do not include numeric value.
    - rid: 5530781212759556336
      type: {class: Comment, ns: UnityEngine.Localization.Metadata, asm: Unity.Localization}
      data:
        m_CommentText: Description explaining what credits are and how they are used.
          Keep concise (~120 chars).
    - rid: 5530781212759556337
      type: {class: Comment, ns: UnityEngine.Localization.Metadata, asm: Unity.Localization}
      data:
        m_CommentText: Title for 'Chrome' resource shown in UI. Short label (<=12
          chars).
    - rid: 5530781212759556338
      type: {class: Comment, ns: UnityEngine.Localization.Metadata, asm: Unity.Localization}
      data:
        m_CommentText: 'Description for Chrome resource: explain use (e.g., upgrade,
          crafting). Keep concise (~120 chars).'
    - rid: 5530781212759556339
      type: {class: Comment, ns: UnityEngine.Localization.Metadata, asm: Unity.Localization}
      data:
        m_CommentText: Title for a healing pack/consumable. Single-word or short
          phrase preferred.
    - rid: 5530781212759556340
      type: {class: Comment, ns: UnityEngine.Localization.Metadata, asm: Unity.Localization}
      data:
        m_CommentText: 'Description for heal pack: amount or effect summary. Avoid
